Question: At least one panda is lying on its back.

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the panda lying on its back?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the panda lying on its back?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} or {ANSWER1}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
